data.description: Welcome to Canyon Creek! This farmhouse style hilltop view property sits on a 1/2 acre lot with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. A spacious open floor plan for the family to enjoy and entertain guests. Granite countertops throughout the kitchen, bathrooms and laundry. Large primary suite completed with dual vanities, whirlpool tub, oversized walk-in closet and shower. Large covered patio area to entertain with full privacy from the mature trees along the back portion of the property. Upgraded chandelier light fixtures throughout the living areas. Large 12 person storm shelter. Shop building allowed in Neighborhood. Assumable VA Loan
